data.description: This exquisite townhome is located in the high demand Hunters Wood development in Apple Valley.  The home features main level living filled with natural sunlight, an exceptional owner’s suite, three additional bedrooms, and three bathrooms. The spacious kitchen features maple cabinetry with stainless steel appliances, quartz counters, beautifully refinished maple flooring, and fantastic wooded views from the maintenance free deck! The lower levels offer a recreation room with a wet bar, a sizable family room with a gas fireplace, a walk-out to the second deck, oversized windows for natural light, an office, workshop, and amusement room with a putting green!  Make this home yours today!
